<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Evently - Registration Success</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: "Poppins", Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f5f7fa;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        padding: 20px 0;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        overflow: hidden;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        min-height: 500px;
      }

      /* Header */
      .header {
        background: #4caf50;
        color: white;
        padding: 32px 24px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .header h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }

      /* Content */
      .content {
        flex: 1;
        padding: 32px 24px;
      }

      .content p {
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        color: #374151;
        font-size: 15px;
      }

      .info-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 20px 0 32px 0;
        background: #f9fafb;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .info-list li {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 8px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .info-list li:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }

      .info-label {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #374151;
      }

      .info-value {
        color: #6b7280;
      }

      /* Button */
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #4caf50;
        color: white !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 14px 28px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 15px;
        transition: background 0.2s ease;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }

      .button:hover {
        background: #388e3c;
      }

      /* Footer */
      .footer {
        background: #f9fafb;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #9ca3af;
        padding: 16px;
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }

      /* Responsiveness */
      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        body {
          padding: 10px 0;
        }

        .container {
          margin: 0 10px;
          border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .header {
          padding: 24px 16px;
        }

        .header h1 {
          font-size: 20px;
        }

        .content {
          padding: 24px 16px;
        }

        .info-list {
          padding: 16px;
        }

        .info-list li {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
          gap: 4px;
        }

        .info-value {
          text-align: left;
          font-weight: 500;
        }

        .button {
          width: 100%;
          text-align: center;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .container {
          margin: 0 5px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Evently</h1>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="content">
        <p>Halo <%= username %>,</p>
        <p>Terima kasih telah mendaftar di Evently. Berikut adalah informasi akun Anda:</p>

        <ul class="info-list">
          <li>
            <span class="info-label">Nama</span>
            <span class="info-value"><%= username %></span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="info-label">Email</span>
            <span class="info-value"><%= email %></span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="info-label">Tanggal Registrasi</span>
            <span class="info-value"> <%= new Date(createdAt).toLocaleDateString("id-ID", { day:"2-digit", month:"long", year:"numeric" }) %> </span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <p>Untuk memulai penggunaan Evently, silakan klik tombol berikut untuk verifikasi akun Anda.</p>

        <a href="<%= activationLink %>" class="button">Aktifkan Akun</a>

        <p>Jika Anda memiliki pertanyaan atau masalah, jangan ragu untuk menghubungi kami.</p>

        <p>Terima kasih telah bergabung dengan Evently!</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2025 Evently. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
